- @link_color = "#137AC2"

!!!
%html
  %head
    %meta{ 'content' => "text/html; charset=UTF-8", 'http-equiv' => "Content-Type" }

  %body{:style => "background:url(http://givebrand.to/assets/bg2.png) #f6f6f6;font-size:12px;font-family:Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;margin:0;padding:15px 0 0;line-height:1.4;"}
    %table{:style => "margin: 0 auto;width:600px;"}
      %tbody
        = render 'user_mailer/header'

    %table{:style => "background:#fff;margin: 0 auto;padding:20px;text-align:center;width:600px;"}
      %tbody

        %tr
          %td
            %h1{:style => "color:#582a00;margin:10px 0 5px;font-size:24px;"} #{@receiver.name}! Check it OUT!
            %p{:style => "font-size:12px;line-height:1.4;color:#444;margin:0 0 15px;"}
              #{link_to @endorser.name, me_user_url(@endorser), :style => "color: #{@link_color};"} has just left an endorsement on your GiveBrand profile. Take a look:
            %p{:style => "font-size:12px;font-style:italic;line-height:1.4;color:#444;margin:0 0 15px;"}
              = @endorsement.description

        %tr
          %td{:colspan => "100"}
            %hr{:style => "background:none;border:none;border-top:1px solid #f8f8f8;"}
        %tr
          %td
            %p{:style => "font-size:11px;line-height:1.4;color:#444;margin:0 0 15px;"}
              How nice is that?! Now, why not #{link_to 'invite', invite_url, :style => "color: #{@link_color};"} some more people to GiveBrand and keep this love fest going?

    = render 'user_mailer/footer'
